.TH "ibmvmc_reset" 9 "ibmvmc_reset" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
ibmvmc_reset \- Reset
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "void" ibmvmc_reset
.BI "(struct crq_server_adapter *adapter "  ","
.BI "bool xport_event "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "adapter" 12
crq_server_adapter struct
.IP "xport_event" 12
If true, the partner closed their CRQ; we don't need to reset.
If false, we need to schedule a CRQ reset.
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Closes all HMC sessions and conditionally schedules a CRQ reset.
